'''Idurar n Ahaggar''' (s [[tifinaɣ|tfinaɣ]]: '''ⴰⴱⴴⴴⴰⵔ''') d yiwen [[Azrar n idurar|azrar n idurar]] i d-ezgan di tlemmast n [[Aneẓč
Uneẓruf Ameqran|Uneẓruf Ameqqran]] swaswa deg unẓul asemran n tmurt n [[Lezzayer]]. Tajumma-ines tessaweḍ ɣer 550.000 km² (ayen yegdan ⅕ n tjumma tummidt n Lezzayer), yerna yeẓẓel ɣef [[asaneṭ n uxenẓir|usaneṭ n uxenẓir]] i d-t-ibeṭṭun ɣef ugafa.

==Isem==

[[Imucaɣ]] neɣ Imajeɣen ([[Imaziɣen]] n Uhaggar) ssawalen i yidurar-nni (''Idurar Uhaggar''), D isem i d-yekkan seg wawal Ahaggar ([[asget]]: ''Ihaggaren'') i wumi qqaren Ihaggaren (Inublen/Ccerfa) gar Imucaɣ n temnaṭ-a.

==Tarakalt==

Tamnaṭ tamedrart n Uhaggar ɣur-es tajumma azal n 540 000 km2, ugar tin n [[Fransa]]. 
Taqacuct n yidurar-a tella d Tahat, deg 3004 lmitrat af yilel.  

